name: Victoria Box
description: The Victoria Box is a chic accent piece for your home. The piece is bejeweled with an elegant handle that has semi precious stone inserts. This piece comes in 2 sizes and 2 finishes. Currently made to order 5-6 weeks. Handmade. Shagreen, Semi-Precious Stone, & Bronze-Patina Brass. Rectangle-22 x 13 x 7.5 cm, Square-18 x 18 x 7.5 cm. Wipe clean with soft dry cloth. Made in Philippines. Inspired by her parents, Kifu's collection of Home Accessories and Furniture has a distinct identity of its own, featuring handmade techniques and intricate inlay patterns.
